branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The floating joint series JA (standard) and JAH (heavy duty), can absorb any &quot;off-centering&quot; or &quot;loss of parallel accuracy&quot; between the cylinder and the driven body. Because of this, centering is unnecessary, installation time is drastically reduced, and a high level of machining accuracy is unnecessary.
&lt;/p&gt;

